          "locale": {
            "fi-fi": {
              "display_title": "SPLITFACE",
              "description": "”Sankarit, toivottavasti kuulette tämän viestin! SPLITFACE on karannut ja yrittää nyt tuhota Hero Factoryn viestintäyhteydet. Ottakaa mukaanne mitä ikinä tarvitsette, tällä jakomielisellä tyypillä on repivät kynnet, plasma-ase ja tarkka laser. Pysäyttäkää hänet keinolla millä hyvänsä. Ette saa epäonnistua!”",
              "title": "SPLITFACE",
              "tags": []
            },
            "en-us": {
              "bullet_points": "•  Features shredding claw, plasma gun with shooter, precision laser and dual-face mask\r\n•  Highly flexible and poseable elements\r\n•  Fire the plasma gun shooter!\r\n•  Includes unique code worth 300 game points for LEGO Hero Factory BREAKOUT game\r\n•  Battle with the hero 6217 SURGE!\r\n•  Combine with 6217 SURGE for an even bigger model!\r\n•  Stands over 7” (18cm) tall!",
              "display_title": "SPLITFACE",
              "description": "“Heroes, we hope you’re receiving this message! SPLITFACE has escaped and is trying to disrupt Hero Factory communications. Equip yourselves with anything you need to combat his vicious shredding claw, plasma gun, precision laser and split personality and stop him before it’s too late. Failure is not an option!”",
              "title": "SPLITFACE",
              "headline": "Evade capture with SPLITFACE’s shredding claws and split personality!",
